      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent v2022R2 is used under an FDA-recognized software quality assurance framework. Version control, regression testing, and release documentation are maintained. SQA procedures verified against ASME V&V 40 Table 3 Gradation 2 requirements.",
      "acceptanceCriteria": {
